You'll love all the space, with its 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, utility room with lots of cabinet space, playroom, large enclosed sunroom/office/craft room, workshop off the garage and more. Plenty of parking with the circle driveway and extra large driveway. Call today for an appointment
